name: 克洛伊·罗曼斯基
name_full: 克洛伊·罗曼斯基 Chloe Romanski
introduction: Chloe Romanski was born June 20th 2007. She is known for Voices and Peel. She is a 1st degree black belt with close to 30 titles. She loves people and animals! She one day hopes to become a scientist and find a cure to cancer! Chloe loves to act and model. She takes weekly lessons and is always working to be a better actress.克洛伊·罗曼斯基于2007年6月20日出生。她以《voices》和《Peel》闻名。她是一级黑带，拥有近30个头衔。她喜爱人和动物！她希望有一天能成为一名科学家，找到治疗癌症的方法！克洛伊喜欢表演和当模特。她每周都上课，并总是努力成为一个更好的演员。
